description: This file contains utility functions for extracting and formatting version information from a provided dictionary. It defines two main functions: GetVersion, which parses the version details from input info, and GetVersionString, which returns a string representation of the version.

methods.name: GetVersion(info)
methods.description: Extracts and returns a list of [major, minor, patch] version numbers from the provided info dictionary.

methods.name: GetVersionString(info)
methods.description: Returns a string representation of the version, obtained by calling GetVersion and joining its components with dots.
